    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Seven PT/Rehab Units from six earthquake affected districts including equipment and human resources establish and run to deliver rehab services;Capacity building of staffs assigned at PT/Rehab units;Cash support to 110 poor and most vulnerable clients;Conduct /arrange outreach camps to reach remote and less accessible places;Develop tools and forms for assessment, treatment, referral, discharge, SoP for PT/Rehab unit, SoP for step down facility etc;Conduct inception meeting, review meetings, field visits, CPAC meeting, lesson learned ws and final evaluation as a monitoring and evaluation perspective;Develop MCM plan at district and PHCC at Nuwakot including roster update and test by drill;Trainings to hospital staffs on PTC/ETM/ Emergency Logistic to response mass casualty incidents;Pre-positioning of assistive devices / mobility devices to hub hospitals topping up on WHO supplies;"
      },
